This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the learning capabilities of neural networks. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it discusses the ability of neural networks to learn fundamental relations. Additionally, it could be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it focuses on the development of neural networks. The paper also mentions the use of neural networks in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), so these sub-categories are also likely.
